PrecisORDER respecting the WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL of CERTAIN LANDS in the YUKON TERRITORY (SELKIRK FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of certain lands in the Yukon in order to facilitate the settlement of Aboriginal land claims, and (b) the repeal of an earlier Withdrawal Order (P.C. 1997-594).

precis:
ORDER respecting the WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL of CERTAIN LANDS in the YUKON
TERRITORY (SELKIRK FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which provides for (a) the
withdrawal from disposal of certain lands in the Yukon in order to
facilitate the settlement of Aboriginal land claims, and (b) the repeal of
an earlier Withdrawal Order (P.C. 1997-594).
